  <brief_title>Long-term Follow-up of Incisional Hernia Repaired With Intraperitoneal Mesh</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Study of Long-term Follow-up of Incisional Hernia Repaired With Intraperitoneal Mesh Versus On-lay Mesh Repair</official_title>
